Highlights
We at Meta want you to understand what information we collect, and how we use and share it. That‚Äôs why we encourage you to read our Privacy Policy. This helps you use
Meta Products
in the way that‚Äôs right for you.
In the Privacy Policy, we explain how we collect, use, share, retain and transfer information. We also let you know your rights. Each section of this Policy includes helpful examples and simpler language to make our practices easier to understand. We‚Äôve also added links to resources where you can learn more about the privacy topics that interest you.
It's important to us that you know how to control your privacy, so we also show you where you can manage your information in the settings of the Meta Products you use. You can
update these settings
to shape your experience.
Read the full Policy below.
